column5: WELL WITH STUPIDITY ON MY SIDE I VENTURED OUT THIS MORN!!! AFTER 2 NEAR HEAD ONS AND A 360 ON THE 401 WE MADE IT FISHIN BY 7:30AM!!!  LOTS OF SLUSH AND ICE!!! AROUND 11ISH THEY STARTED TO HIT!!!  I WENT 3FOR5 !! NOT BAD CONSIDERING THE CONS LOL  I THINK I'LL STAY HOME TOMORROW  LOL
Nice fish as usual CC. Becareful out there. With the slush on the roads and tonights temps dropping down to -13 to -14 everything will freeze up .   dsn
Man CC your worst days are 3 times better than my best days, lol  Glad you got there and back safe & sound! With fish to boot!
CC  nice crome!!! thanks for sharing!  Gerritt.
glad to see you are taming that steel. Thanks for the report
